HOW TO MEASURE

Bust Measure under your arms at the fullest part of your bust. Be sure to go over your shoulder blades.
Waist Measure around the narrowest part of your waistline with one forefinger between your body and the measuring tape.
Hips Stand with your feet together and measure around the fullest part of your hips.

Desc

Designed in collaboration with Entire Studios, this is a puffer vest with a boxy, oversized fit and a removable hood. Made from a smooth, coated fabric with a matte finish and an alternative down fill.

Details

Details

  • Boxy oversized fit
  • Removable hood
  • Cinchable hood with snap closure
  • Hidden zipper chest pockets
  • Zipper and velcro closure
  • Cinchable hem
  • Interior zip pocket
